<div class="dablink">This article is about flash-based, DRAM-based and other solid-state drives.  For other flash-based solid-state storage, see <a href="/wiki/USB_flash_drive" title="USB flash drive">USB flash drive</a>.  For software based secondary storage, see <a href="/wiki/RAM_disk" title="RAM disk">RAM disk</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:172px;"><a href="/wiki/File:E-disk_2-5_scsi.jpg" class="image" title="An SSD in standard 2.5-inch (64&#160;mm) form-factor."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/95/E-disk_2-5_scsi.jpg" width="170" height="122" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:E-disk_2-5_scsi.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
